WEBVTT

00:00:00.964 --> 00:00:03.702
Narrator:
PREVIOUSLY ON "YU-GI-OH"...

00:00:03.702 --> 00:00:05.772
LET'S FOCUS
ON THE PHARAOH.

00:00:05.772 --> 00:00:07.609
ONCE WE GET HIM
OUT OF THE WAY,

00:00:07.609 --> 00:00:09.779
THE OTHERS
WILL FALL RIGHT
INTO OUR HANDS,

00:00:09.779 --> 00:00:11.249
ONE BY ONE.

00:00:11.249 --> 00:00:13.486
BUT HOW DO YA KNOW
THE PHARAOH WILL DUEL?

00:00:13.486 --> 00:00:16.057
BECAUSE MY PLAN IS
ALREADY IN PLACE.

00:00:16.057 --> 00:00:18.160
IT'S ONLY
A MATTER OF TIME.

00:00:18.160 --> 00:00:20.298
Yugi, voice-over:
I KNOW WHAT I HAFTA DO.

00:00:20.298 --> 00:00:24.739
TIME TO FACE THESE CREEPS.

00:00:24.739 --> 00:00:29.281
WE CAN'T MISS THE SHOWDOWN
BETWEEN YUGI AND THOSE GUYS.

00:00:29.281 --> 00:00:30.349
IT'S YUGI.

00:00:30.349 --> 00:00:32.720
HE'S GETTING AHEAD.

00:00:32.720 --> 00:00:33.889
NO!

00:00:33.889 --> 00:00:36.192
PUT THE PEDAL
TO THE METAL.

00:00:41.101 --> 00:00:43.973
Man:
I'M READY FOR YOU, PHARAOH,

00:00:43.973 --> 00:00:48.014
THANKS TO MY DECK
AND THE POWER IT HOLDS.

00:00:55.828 --> 00:00:57.264
♪ YOUR MOVE, YOUR MOVE,
YOUR MOVE ♪

00:00:57.264 --> 00:00:58.700
♪ YOUR MOVE, YOUR MOVE ♪

00:00:58.700 --> 00:01:00.002
♪ YOUR MOVE! ♪

00:01:02.773 --> 00:01:04.744
♪ YU-GI-OH! ♪

00:01:21.172 --> 00:01:22.676
♪ YOUR MOVE! ♪

00:01:25.079 --> 00:01:27.050
♪ YU-GI-OH! ♪

00:01:28.786 --> 00:01:31.624
IT'S TIME TO D-D-DUEL!

00:01:46.684 --> 00:01:49.222
♪ YU-GI-OH! ♪

00:01:57.638 --> 00:01:59.607
Duke, voice-over:
BUCKLE UP, BOYS.

00:01:59.607 --> 00:02:03.281
[CHEERING]

00:02:03.281 --> 00:02:06.152
WHO NEEDS ROADS
WHEN YA GOT ONE A
DESE BAD BOYS?

00:02:06.152 --> 00:02:09.158
YEAH, NOW STEP ON IT
SO WE CAN FIND YUGI.

00:02:09.158 --> 00:02:10.260
10-4.

00:02:10.260 --> 00:02:12.197
HANG ON, FELLAS.

00:02:14.234 --> 00:02:15.703
WHOA!

00:02:18.508 --> 00:02:22.248
[SHOUTING]

00:02:22.248 --> 00:02:24.819
Joey: MOMMY!

00:02:24.819 --> 00:02:28.993
ARE YOU TWO
STILL IN ONE PIECE?

00:02:28.993 --> 00:02:30.662
THEY'RE IN NO PIECE!

00:02:37.275 --> 00:02:41.047
I TOLD THEM TO BUCKLE UP.

00:02:41.047 --> 00:02:43.185
MAYBE WE'RE SAFER
ON FOOT.

00:02:43.185 --> 00:02:45.823
GIMME A PIGGY BACK
AND YOU GOT A DEAL.

00:02:55.072 --> 00:02:59.514
Man, voice-over:
THE PHARAOH SHOULD BE
ARRIVING SHORTLY

00:02:59.514 --> 00:03:01.985
FOR HIS FINAL DUEL.

00:03:05.759 --> 00:03:07.295
LET'S DO THIS!

00:03:07.295 --> 00:03:09.197
[WHINNYING]

00:03:18.582 --> 00:03:22.054
Man:
VERY IMPRESSIVE, COWBOY,

00:03:22.054 --> 00:03:24.358
BUT YOU'LL NEED MORE
THAN A FEW RODEO TRICKS

00:03:24.358 --> 00:03:30.269
TO GET YOURSELF
OUTTA THIS.

00:03:30.269 --> 00:03:32.940
YOU SEE,
WHILE MY ASSOCIATES
ARE SATISFIED

00:03:32.940 --> 00:03:36.847
WITH STEALING THE SOULS
OF YOUR FRIENDS, I'M NOT.

00:03:36.847 --> 00:03:39.785
I DID MY PART.

00:03:39.785 --> 00:03:42.090
NOW RELEASE
THE PROFESSOR
AS YOU PROMISED.

00:03:42.090 --> 00:03:45.362
HE'S ALREADY
BEEN SET FREE,

00:03:45.362 --> 00:03:47.899
BUT SINCE YOU'VE COME
ALL THIS WAY,

00:03:47.899 --> 00:03:50.237
YOU MIGHT AS WELL
STAY AWHILE.

00:04:04.462 --> 00:04:07.435
SO YOU'RE GONNA
STICK AROUND, RIGHT?

00:04:07.435 --> 00:04:09.906
'CAUSE LIKE I SAID
BEFORE PHARAOH,

00:04:09.906 --> 00:04:11.509
YOUR FRIENDS
AREN'T GOOD ENOUGH.

00:04:11.509 --> 00:04:16.351
I NEED TO CAPTURE THE SOUL
OF THE PHARAOH HIMSELF

00:04:16.351 --> 00:04:18.554
SO I CAN SAVE THE WORLD.

00:04:18.554 --> 00:04:20.758
SAVE THE WORLD?

00:04:20.758 --> 00:04:22.594
DON'T YOU SEE
THAT WHAT YOU'RE DOING

00:04:22.594 --> 00:04:24.331
IS GOING TO
DESTROY THE WORLD?

00:04:24.331 --> 00:04:27.637
OR ARE YOU SO INSANE
THAT YOU CAN'T TELL
THE DIFFERENCE?

00:04:27.637 --> 00:04:29.407
I'M JUST FINE.

00:04:29.407 --> 00:04:32.245
IT'S YOU WHO'S BLIND
TO WHAT'S GOING ON.

00:04:32.245 --> 00:04:34.182
YOU'RE FIGHTING
ON THE WRONG SIDE.

00:04:34.182 --> 00:04:35.985
EXPLAIN YOURSELF.

00:04:35.985 --> 00:04:39.224
THIS WORLD'S A DARK
AND LONELY PLACE TO LIVE.

00:04:39.224 --> 00:04:41.829
IT'S BEEN POISONED
BY MANKIND.

00:04:41.829 --> 00:04:46.337
ALL I'M TRYING TO DO
IS FIX WHAT'S BEEN RUINED
BY PEOPLE LIKE YOU,

00:04:46.337 --> 00:04:49.744
AND I'LL DO IT
BY LOCKING YOUR SPIRIT
AWAY FOR GOOD.

00:04:49.744 --> 00:04:51.546
WHO DO YOU THINK
YOU ARE?

00:04:51.546 --> 00:04:53.449
LOOK, THE NAME'S RAFAEL,

00:04:53.449 --> 00:04:56.589
AND I CALLED YOU HERE TO DUEL,
NOT SHOOT THE BREEZE.

00:04:56.589 --> 00:04:58.860
I'VE WAITED FOR THIS MOMENT
LONG ENOUGH

00:04:58.860 --> 00:05:02.365
AND I HAVE NO INTENTION
OF PUTTING OUR FIGHT OFF
FOR ANOTHER MINUTE,

00:05:02.365 --> 00:05:07.307
SO LET'S GO.

00:05:07.307 --> 00:05:09.545
YOU'VE GIVEN ME
NO CHOICE.

00:05:09.545 --> 00:05:11.014
BUT KNOW THIS,

00:05:11.014 --> 00:05:13.118
IN THE END,
RIGHTEOUSNESS
WILL PREVAIL

00:05:13.118 --> 00:05:15.288
AND JUSTICE
SHALL BE SERVED.

00:05:15.288 --> 00:05:18.461
THAT'S JUST WHAT
I'M HOPING FOR.

00:05:18.461 --> 00:05:20.464
Both: LET'S DUEL!

00:05:30.114 --> 00:05:33.419
Yugi, voice-over:
SOMETHING SEEMS DIFFERENT
ABOUT THIS GUY.

00:05:33.419 --> 00:05:34.889
Yami-yugi, voice-over:
I AGREE, YUGI.

00:05:34.889 --> 00:05:37.527
HE HAS SOME SORT OF
HIDDEN POWER.

00:05:37.527 --> 00:05:40.065
I'LL START THINGS OFF,
IF YA DON'T MIND,

00:05:40.065 --> 00:05:44.906
BY PLAYING A MAGIC CARD
KNOWN AS GUARDIAN TREASURE.

00:05:44.906 --> 00:05:46.910
IT ALLOWS ME TO DRAW
TWO NEW CARDS

00:05:46.910 --> 00:05:49.748
AS LONG AS I TOSS OUT
THE 5 THAT ARE IN MY HAND.

00:05:49.748 --> 00:05:53.922
PLUS, I CAN DRAW 2 MORE CARDS
EVERY ROUND FROM NOW ON.

00:05:53.922 --> 00:05:55.426
Yugi, voice-over:
I DON'T GET IT.

00:05:55.426 --> 00:05:59.031
WHY WOULD HE GET RID
OF HIS ENTIRE HAND
JUST FOR THAT?

00:05:59.031 --> 00:06:01.703
HE'S SEARCHING FOR
THE SEAL OF ORICHALCOS!

00:06:01.703 --> 00:06:04.508
I SUMMON A MONSTER
IN DEFENSE MODE,

00:06:04.508 --> 00:06:07.380
AND THEN I PLACE
ONE CARD FACE DOWN
ON THE FIELD.

00:06:07.380 --> 00:06:08.816
THAT ENDS MY TURN.

00:06:08.816 --> 00:06:11.921
YOU OUGHTTA BE
THANKING ME, PHARAOH.

00:06:11.921 --> 00:06:14.359
I JUST GAVE YOU
A HEAD START.

00:06:14.359 --> 00:06:16.096
SINCE I PLAYED TWO CARDS,

00:06:16.096 --> 00:06:17.932
I HAVE NOTHING LEFT
IN MY HAND.

00:06:17.932 --> 00:06:20.036
Yugi, voice-over:
HE MAY BE TOYING WITH ME,

00:06:20.036 --> 00:06:21.605
BUT HE DOES HAVE A POINT.

00:06:21.605 --> 00:06:23.541
IF I DESTROY
HIS DEFENSIVE MONSTER,

00:06:23.541 --> 00:06:25.512
I CAN TAKE AN EARLY LEAD.

00:06:25.512 --> 00:06:27.115
Yami-yugi: HERE GOES!

00:06:30.888 --> 00:06:34.128
I FUSE TOGETHER
GAZELLE AND BERFOMET

00:06:34.128 --> 00:06:36.464
IN ORDER
TO FORM CHIMERA,

00:06:36.464 --> 00:06:40.939
THE FLYING
MYTHICAL BEAST!

00:06:40.939 --> 00:06:42.943
I'M SURE
YOUR DEFENSIVE MONSTER

00:06:42.943 --> 00:06:45.948
WON'T STAND A CHANCE
AGAINST CHIMERA.

00:06:45.948 --> 00:06:48.987
NOW, MY MYTHICAL BEAST,
ATTACK!

00:06:55.598 --> 00:06:59.072
[RAFAEL LAUGHS]

00:06:59.072 --> 00:07:03.880
NOW WHAT WERE YOU SAYING
ABOUT MY MONSTER
NOT STANDING A CHANCE?

00:07:06.552 --> 00:07:11.527
MY BACKUP GARDNA
HAS MORE THAN ENOUGH DEFENSE
POINTS TO STOP YOU.

00:07:16.937 --> 00:07:19.675
BACK TO ME.

00:07:19.675 --> 00:07:23.615
I ACTIVATE
THE MAGIC CARD
GRAVITY AXE.

00:07:23.615 --> 00:07:28.390
THIS ALLOWS ME TO SUMMON
AN ALL-POWERFUL MONSTER,

00:07:28.390 --> 00:07:32.564
SO MEET GUARDIAN GRARL!

00:07:32.564 --> 00:07:36.738
AND IF YOU THINK
MY MONSTER'S STRONG NOW,
JUST WAIT,

00:07:36.738 --> 00:07:38.742
'CAUSE WHEN I ADD
GRAVITY AXE,

00:07:38.742 --> 00:07:43.651
MY GUARDIAN GRARL
GAINS AN ADDITIONAL
500 ATTACK POINTS.

00:07:43.651 --> 00:07:45.487
3,000 POINTS?

00:07:45.487 --> 00:07:49.361
NOW, GUARDIAN GRARL,
ATTACK CHIMERA.

00:07:55.438 --> 00:07:57.275
MY MONSTER
MAY BE GONE NOW,

00:07:57.275 --> 00:07:59.379
BUT HIS SPECIAL ABILITY
REMAINS.

00:07:59.379 --> 00:08:02.952
OBSERVE!

00:08:02.952 --> 00:08:04.521
BIG DEAL.

00:08:04.521 --> 00:08:06.024
SO YOUR
TWO-HEADED PIPSQUEAK

00:08:06.024 --> 00:08:08.795
LEFT BEHIND
AN EVEN WEAKER MONSTER.

00:08:08.795 --> 00:08:09.931
I'M SHAKIN'.

00:08:09.931 --> 00:08:11.567
YOU SHOULD BE.

00:08:11.567 --> 00:08:14.372
I'M AFRAID
YOU'RE GONNA HAFTA DO
BETTER THAN THAT,

00:08:14.372 --> 00:08:17.110
'CAUSE I HAVE A DECK
FULL OF GUARDIAN MONSTERS

00:08:17.110 --> 00:08:19.515
AND EACH ONE
IS MORE POWERFUL
THAN THE NEXT.

00:08:19.515 --> 00:08:22.553
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
GUARDIAN MONSTERS?

00:08:27.495 --> 00:08:29.465
Tea: PROFESSOR HAWKINS?

00:08:33.505 --> 00:08:36.043
YOUR GRAMPS
HAS THE RIGHT IDEA.

00:08:36.043 --> 00:08:37.614
WE COULD ALL USE
A COUPLE 'A Zs.

00:08:37.614 --> 00:08:39.350
Rebecca: NOT ME.

00:08:39.350 --> 00:08:41.387
I'VE BEEN DOING
SOME RESEARCH
ON THE WEB

00:08:41.387 --> 00:08:43.290
AND I THINK
I'M ON TO SOMETHING.

00:08:43.290 --> 00:08:44.759
WAIT A SEC.

00:08:44.759 --> 00:08:46.796
YOU'RE NOT TRADING
DUEL MONSTERS CARDS
AGAIN, ARE YOU?

00:08:46.796 --> 00:08:49.601
NO. I FOUND THIS
STRANGE ARTICLE.

00:08:49.601 --> 00:08:52.673
IT'S ABOUT A CRUISE SHIP
THAT SUNK ABOUT 12 AGO

00:08:52.673 --> 00:08:56.681
AND A BOY WHO SAVED HIMSELF
BY SWIMMING TO AN ISLAND.

00:08:56.681 --> 00:09:01.322
HE SPENT 3 YEARS
OF HIS LIFE ALL ALONE
ON THAT DESERTED ISLAND.

00:09:01.322 --> 00:09:03.226
AND ACCORDING TO THIS STORY,

00:09:03.226 --> 00:09:05.562
HE DID NOTHING BUT PRACTICE
PLAYING DUEL MONSTERS

00:09:05.562 --> 00:09:08.669
OVER AND OVER AGAIN
UNTIL HE WAS RESCUED.

00:09:08.669 --> 00:09:12.074
AND GET THIS,
HIS NAME WAS RAFAEL.

00:09:12.074 --> 00:09:13.644
THE GUY
WHO'S DUELING YUGI?

00:09:13.644 --> 00:09:15.647
EXACTLY.

00:09:15.647 --> 00:09:16.649
WAIT!

00:09:16.649 --> 00:09:17.851
LET GO OF ME!

00:09:17.851 --> 00:09:20.089
RELAX, REBECCA.

00:09:20.089 --> 00:09:21.858
YUGI CAN HANDLE
THAT GUY.

00:09:21.858 --> 00:09:26.834
YOU SURE?

00:09:26.834 --> 00:09:31.943
YOU COULD NEVER UNDERSTAND
THE CONNECTION I HAVE
WITH MY CARDS, PHARAOH.

00:09:31.943 --> 00:09:34.081
I'M AFRAID
YOU'RE MISTAKEN.

00:09:34.081 --> 00:09:36.585
I ALSO SHARE A BOND
WITH MY DECK.

00:09:36.585 --> 00:09:39.457
I TRUST AND RESPECT
EVERY ONE OF MY CARDS.

00:09:39.457 --> 00:09:40.525
OH, YEAH?

00:09:40.525 --> 00:09:43.964
WELL, TAKE A LOOK
AT THESE.

00:09:43.964 --> 00:09:45.266
Yugi, voice-over: WHOA!

00:09:45.266 --> 00:09:48.004
HIS CARDS ARE ALMOST
COMPLETELY WORN OUT.

00:09:48.004 --> 00:09:50.609
I'VE PLAYED THESE CARDS
HUNDREDS OF TIMES,

00:09:50.609 --> 00:09:52.380
AND EVEN THOUGH
THEY'RE FALLING APART,

00:09:52.380 --> 00:09:54.116
I'LL NEVER REPLACE THEM.

00:09:54.116 --> 00:09:58.123
I'VE SWORN TO PROTECT THEM
THE WAY THEY PROTECTED ME,

00:09:58.123 --> 00:10:02.765
'CAUSE 12 YEARS AGO,
THESE MONSTERS SAVED MY LIFE.

00:10:06.769 --> 00:10:07.938
WHEN I WAS A KID,

00:10:07.938 --> 00:10:09.240
I WAS FOOLED INTO BELIEVING

00:10:09.240 --> 00:10:11.310
THE WORLD WAS A HAPPY PLACE.

00:10:11.310 --> 00:10:13.881
BUT SOON
I DISCOVERED THE TRUTH,

00:10:13.881 --> 00:10:16.754
THAT NOTHING'S FAIR
AND NO ONE GETS
WHAT THEY DESERVE.

00:10:16.754 --> 00:10:18.890
WHAT A SAD WAY
TO SEE THE WORLD.

00:10:18.890 --> 00:10:20.995
YEAH, WELL, LIFE IS SAD,

00:10:20.995 --> 00:10:22.597
AND THE SOONER
YOU REALIZE THAT,

00:10:22.597 --> 00:10:24.233
THE BETTER OFF YOU'LL BE.

00:10:24.233 --> 00:10:25.502
I OUGHTTA KNOW.

00:10:25.502 --> 00:10:28.908
I USED TO HAVE EVERYTHING
A KID COULD EVER WANT,

00:10:28.908 --> 00:10:33.216
UNTIL ONE DAY,
WHEN EVERYTHING
WAS TAKEN AWAY FROM ME.

00:10:33.216 --> 00:10:34.919
Man: DO YOU RECOMMEND
THE ESCARGOT?

00:10:34.919 --> 00:10:37.724
Second man: SO TELL ME
ALL ABOUT YOUR WEEK
IN THE FRENCH RIVIERA.

00:10:37.724 --> 00:10:39.928
Third man:
THE CAVIAR IS SUPERB
TONIGHT, ISN'T IT?

00:10:39.928 --> 00:10:41.264
Fourth man: GARCON,
MORE WATER PLEASE.

00:10:41.264 --> 00:10:42.900
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, RAF!

00:10:42.900 --> 00:10:44.202
A PRESENT?

00:10:44.202 --> 00:10:45.204
COOL.

00:10:45.204 --> 00:10:49.378
C'MON, OPEN IT.

00:10:49.378 --> 00:10:50.447
AWESOME!

00:10:50.447 --> 00:10:52.785
A GUARDIAN EATOS
CARD.

00:10:52.785 --> 00:10:55.189
IT'S PERFECT.
THANKS!

00:10:55.189 --> 00:10:58.227
WE ONLY HAD
TO GO TO 18 STORES
BEFORE WE FOUND IT.

00:10:58.227 --> 00:11:02.034
THAT'S IT?

00:11:02.034 --> 00:11:04.539
DON'T FORGET TO MAKE
YOUR BIRTHDAY WISH, RAFAEL.

00:11:04.539 --> 00:11:05.541
WHAT'S IT GONNA BE?

00:11:05.541 --> 00:11:07.043
NOTHING.

00:11:07.043 --> 00:11:09.280
I ALREADY HAVE
EVERYTHING I NEED.

00:11:09.280 --> 00:11:10.783
[CRASH]

00:11:10.783 --> 00:11:12.686
Man: WE'RE ALL GONERS!

00:11:12.686 --> 00:11:14.255
OH, NO!

00:11:14.255 --> 00:11:16.460
HEY!

00:11:16.460 --> 00:11:18.196
SWEETHEART!

00:11:18.196 --> 00:11:22.036
Rafael, voice-over:
I KNEW SOMETHING WAS WRONG.

00:11:22.036 --> 00:11:24.373
WE WERE HEADING STRAIGHT
FOR A TIDAL WAVE

00:11:24.373 --> 00:11:27.112
AND THERE WAS
NO TURNING BACK.

00:11:27.112 --> 00:11:30.985
[SHOUTING]

00:11:30.985 --> 00:11:33.389
[PEOPLE SHOUTING]

00:11:33.389 --> 00:11:35.861
AAH!

00:11:35.861 --> 00:11:38.098
RAFAEL!

00:11:38.098 --> 00:11:40.369
GUYS, COME BACK!

00:11:40.369 --> 00:11:41.370
QUICK!

00:11:41.370 --> 00:11:43.074
GRAB MY HAND!

00:11:43.074 --> 00:11:44.476
AAH!

00:11:44.476 --> 00:11:48.216
[SHOUTING]

00:11:48.216 --> 00:11:52.590
Rafael, voice-over:
THAT WAS THE LAST TIME
I SAW MY FAMILY.

00:11:52.590 --> 00:11:57.666
AAH!

00:11:57.666 --> 00:11:59.002
Rafael, voice-over:
THE STORM WAS OVER

00:11:59.002 --> 00:12:01.072
JUST AS QUICKLY
AS IT STARTED.

00:12:01.072 --> 00:12:03.343
MY FAMILY MADE IT
ON TO A RESCUE BOAT,

00:12:03.343 --> 00:12:10.689
BUT I WAS LEFT BEHIND.

00:12:10.689 --> 00:12:12.660
Young Rafael: HELLO?

00:12:12.660 --> 00:12:14.696
WHO'S THERE?

00:12:14.696 --> 00:12:19.405
GUARDIAN EATOS!

00:12:19.405 --> 00:12:22.911
I THOUGHT MY MIND
WAS PLAYING TRICKS ON ME,

00:12:22.911 --> 00:12:25.683
BUT SURELY SOMEONE ELSE
WAS ON THIS ISLAND--

00:12:25.683 --> 00:12:30.190
MAYBE EVEN MY FAMILY.

00:12:30.190 --> 00:12:36.803
Young Rafael: MOM! DAD!

00:12:36.803 --> 00:12:41.277
Rafael, voice-over:
IT DIDN'T TAKE LONG FOR
ME TO REALIZE THAT I WAS ALONE.

00:12:41.277 --> 00:12:44.650
EVERYTHING
I ONCE HAD WAS GONE.

00:12:44.650 --> 00:12:45.919
NOOOO!

00:12:45.919 --> 00:12:55.202
Rafael, voice-over:
WHO WOULD WATCH OVER ME NOW?

00:12:55.202 --> 00:12:58.040
ALL I HAD WERE
THE CLOTHES ON MY BACK

00:12:58.040 --> 00:13:06.087
AND MY DUEL MONSTERS CARDS.

00:13:06.087 --> 00:13:08.091
I KNEW I HAD TWO CHOICES:

00:13:08.091 --> 00:13:10.729
SIT AROUND AND FEEL
SORRY FOR MYSELF

00:13:10.729 --> 00:13:12.732
OR TOUGHEN UP AND MOVE ON.

00:13:12.732 --> 00:13:16.740
AND IF I WANTED TO SURVIVE,
THE DECISION WAS SIMPLE.

00:13:16.740 --> 00:13:20.814
THERE WAS NO TIME FOR WEAKNESS.

00:13:20.814 --> 00:13:24.721
I LEARNED AT A YOUNG AGE
THAT THE WORLD
IS COLD AND LONELY.

00:13:24.721 --> 00:13:26.791
I LOST MY CHILDHOOD,

00:13:26.791 --> 00:13:29.195
BUT I GAINED SOMETHING
MORE IMPORTANT:

00:13:29.195 --> 00:13:31.967
THE TRUTH...

00:13:31.967 --> 00:13:36.175
AND AN UNDYING TRUST
FOR THE ONLY FAMILY I HAD,

00:13:36.175 --> 00:13:39.246
MY 3 GUARDIAN CARDS.

00:13:39.246 --> 00:13:44.422
THESE DUEL MONSTERS
WERE EVERYTHING TO ME.

00:13:44.422 --> 00:13:46.092
NO!

00:13:55.909 --> 00:13:58.180
Rafael, voice-over:
THE GUARDIANS KEPT ME STRONG,

00:13:58.180 --> 00:13:59.750
AND SANE.

00:13:59.750 --> 00:14:02.287
THEY SAVED ME
FROM LOSING MY MIND,

00:14:02.287 --> 00:14:07.764
AND I OWED IT TO THOSE CARDS
TO SAVE THEM.

00:14:07.764 --> 00:14:10.001
WE SHARED A POWERFUL BOND.

00:14:17.381 --> 00:14:22.490
GUARDIAN EATOS, GUARDIAN GRARL,
AND GUARDIAN KEY'EST,

00:14:22.490 --> 00:14:26.364
THESE MONSTERS SAW ME
THROUGH THE HARDEST
YEARS OF MY LIFE,

00:14:26.364 --> 00:14:29.069
AND THEY CONTINUE
TO PROTECT ME.

00:14:32.608 --> 00:14:35.513
RAFAEL, IF YOU TRULY
RESPECT YOUR CARDS,

00:14:35.513 --> 00:14:37.651
THEN WHY DO YOU USE
THEM FOR EVIL?

00:14:37.651 --> 00:14:39.287
EVIL, PHARAOH?

00:14:39.287 --> 00:14:41.090
WHAT YOU CONSIDER EVIL

00:14:41.090 --> 00:14:44.262
I LOOK AT
AS SAVING THE PLANET
FROM FALLING APART

00:14:44.262 --> 00:14:47.401
AT THE HANDS
OF PEOPLE LIKE YOU
AND YOUR LITTLE FRIENDS.

00:14:47.401 --> 00:14:51.575
IT'S MY DESTINY.

00:14:51.575 --> 00:14:53.879
I ALWAYS WONDERED, "WHY ME?"

00:14:53.879 --> 00:14:58.988
AND AFTER SPENDING
3 LONG YEARS ON THAT ISLAND,
I FINALLY GOT MY ANSWER.

00:15:04.732 --> 00:15:06.368
HOW COULD I HAVE MISSED IT?

00:15:06.368 --> 00:15:09.473
THERE WAS AN ENTIRE CITY
RIGHT OFF THE COAST.

00:15:09.473 --> 00:15:11.144
I WAS SAVED.

00:15:20.627 --> 00:15:22.363
AAH!

00:15:22.363 --> 00:15:24.100
NOT AGAIN!

00:15:24.100 --> 00:15:26.403
AAH!

00:15:42.165 --> 00:15:43.166
HELLO?

00:15:43.166 --> 00:15:45.604
IS ANYONE DOWN THERE?

00:15:51.114 --> 00:15:53.117
Voice: WELCOME, RAFAEL.

00:15:53.117 --> 00:15:55.655
YOU'VE COME HOME, MY CHILD.

00:15:55.655 --> 00:16:00.030
REMEMBER MY VOICE,
FOR WE SHALL MEET AGAIN.

00:16:00.030 --> 00:16:03.169
Rafael, voice-over: SOON AFTER,
I WOKE UP ON A RESCUE BOAT.

00:16:03.169 --> 00:16:08.678
THEY SAID
THEY FOUND ME UNCONSCIOUS,
FLOATING ON A RAFT.

00:16:08.678 --> 00:16:13.153
I MADE THE COVER
OF NEWSPAPERS AND MAGAZINES
AROUND THE WORLD--

00:16:13.153 --> 00:16:18.029
"MIRACLE BOY REJOINS
CIVILIZATION AFTER BEING
STRANDED FOR YEARS."

00:16:18.029 --> 00:16:19.265
CIVILIZATION?

00:16:19.265 --> 00:16:20.600
PLEASE.

00:16:20.600 --> 00:16:23.739
THE WORLD I CAME BACK TO
WAS ANYTHING BUT CIVILIZED.

00:16:23.739 --> 00:16:26.477
THAT ISLAND
MAY HAVE BEEN LONELY,

00:16:26.477 --> 00:16:29.816
BUT AT LEAST
IT WAS A PEACEFUL
PLACE TO LIVE.

00:16:29.816 --> 00:16:32.354
AND UNLIKE
THE OUTSIDE WORLD,
PHARAOH,

00:16:32.354 --> 00:16:35.893
THERE WAS NO ONE
ON THAT DESERTED ISLAND
WHO COULD WALK OUT ON ME

00:16:35.893 --> 00:16:38.632
LIKE MY FAMILY DID.

00:16:38.632 --> 00:16:41.170
BUT I HAVE
A NEW FAMILY NOW.

00:16:46.344 --> 00:16:47.980
HOW CAN YOU BLAME
MANKIND

00:16:47.980 --> 00:16:49.249
FOR WHAT
HAPPENED TO YOU?

00:16:49.249 --> 00:16:52.989
I TOLD YOU,
PEOPLE ARE EVIL!

00:16:52.989 --> 00:16:55.026
BUT IT WASN'T ALWAYS
THAT WAY.

00:16:55.026 --> 00:16:57.730
ONCE,
THE WORLD WAS PERFECT,

00:16:57.730 --> 00:17:00.536
AND WHEN I GOT BACK
FROM THAT DESERT ISLAND,

00:17:00.536 --> 00:17:04.577
I SAW THIS ANCIENT PARADISE
WITH MY OWN EYES.

00:17:08.784 --> 00:17:11.121
Voice: I TOLD YOU
WE'D MEET AGAIN, RAFAEL.

00:17:11.121 --> 00:17:17.466
NOW, ARE YOU PREPARED TO LEAVE
YOUR OLD LIFE BEHIND?

00:17:17.466 --> 00:17:19.536
[VOICE LAUGHS]

00:17:19.536 --> 00:17:20.838
EXCELLENT.

00:17:20.838 --> 00:17:25.580
TOGETHER, WE SHALL REBUILD
CIVILIZATION AS IT ONCE WAS.

00:17:29.587 --> 00:17:31.458
I DON'T KNOW WHAT LIES
YOU WERE TOLD,

00:17:31.458 --> 00:17:34.396
BUT I KNOW THAT NO GOOD
CAN COME OF YOUR PLAN.

00:17:34.396 --> 00:17:35.965
DON'T WORRY, PHARAOH,

00:17:35.965 --> 00:17:39.004
YOU WON'T BE AROUND
TO SEE HOW MY PLAN TURNS OUT.

00:17:39.004 --> 00:17:40.006
WRONG.

00:17:40.006 --> 00:17:41.208
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

00:17:41.208 --> 00:17:42.810
WE'LL SEE.

00:17:42.810 --> 00:17:44.714
[SCREAMING]

00:17:48.588 --> 00:17:50.825
WELL, SO MUCH
FOR THAT SHORTCUT.

00:17:50.825 --> 00:17:52.562
HEY, CHECK IT OUT.

00:17:52.562 --> 00:17:54.532
YUGI STARTED
DUELING ALREADY.

00:17:54.532 --> 00:17:56.669
IT'S MY MOVE,

00:17:56.669 --> 00:18:02.780
AND NOW I ACTIVATE
THE MAGIC CARD
5 STAR TWILIGHT!

00:18:02.780 --> 00:18:05.151
SINCE I HAVE
A LEVEL 5 MONSTER
IN PLAY,

00:18:05.151 --> 00:18:07.655
MY 5 STAR TWILIGHT
ALLOWS ME TO SUMMON

00:18:07.655 --> 00:18:11.529
5 NEW MONSTERS
TO THE FIELD.

00:18:11.529 --> 00:18:16.905
NOW SAY HELLO TO
AN UNSTOPPABLE FAMILY
OF MONSTERS,

00:18:16.905 --> 00:18:21.045
THE 5 KURIBOH BROTHERS!

00:18:21.045 --> 00:18:25.186
MY CAT'S COUGHED UP
MORE FRIGHTENING THINGS
THAN THOSE MONSTERS.

00:18:25.186 --> 00:18:27.256
LOOKS CAN BE
QUITE DECEIVING.

00:18:27.256 --> 00:18:31.832
GOOOOO, MY KURIBOHS!

00:18:31.832 --> 00:18:33.935
COMBINE YOUR POWERS
TOGETHER

00:18:33.935 --> 00:18:37.842
TO FORM KURIBABYLON!

00:18:37.842 --> 00:18:41.515
NEXT, I ACTIVATE
MY PUMP UP MAGIC CARD.

00:18:41.515 --> 00:18:44.855
ITS POWER WILL NOW
DOUBLE MY KURIBABYLON'S
ATTACK POINTS

00:18:44.855 --> 00:18:47.359
FOR A SINGLE TURN.

00:18:47.359 --> 00:18:51.366
NOW, MY BEAST, ATTACK
WITH HORN OF CHAOS!

00:18:51.366 --> 00:18:53.569
I DON'T THINK SO,
KING PUFF BALL!

00:18:53.569 --> 00:18:56.842
GO, RESCUER FROM THE GRAVE!

00:18:56.842 --> 00:18:59.380
YOU CAN'T PLAY A CARD
FROM YOUR GRAVEYARD.

00:18:59.380 --> 00:19:02.987
I JUST DID.

00:19:02.987 --> 00:19:06.192
THIS POWERFUL MAGIC CARD
CAN ONLY BE ACTIVATED

00:19:06.192 --> 00:19:08.196
ONCE IT'S IN
MY CARD GRAVEYARD,

00:19:08.196 --> 00:19:09.799
AND THEN COMES
THE FUN PART--

00:19:09.799 --> 00:19:11.368
WELL, FUN FOR ME.

00:19:11.368 --> 00:19:15.442
IT INSTANTLY STOPS
YOUR MONSTER'S ATTACK.

00:19:15.442 --> 00:19:16.978
Yugi, voice-over:
THAT MUST BE
WHY HE TOSSED OUT

00:19:16.978 --> 00:19:19.082
HIS WHOLE HAND BEFORE.

00:19:19.082 --> 00:19:21.720
SO WHERE WAS I?

00:19:21.720 --> 00:19:23.623
OH, RIGHT,
I REMEMBER NOW--

00:19:23.623 --> 00:19:27.297
DESTROYING YOU
BY SEALING AWAY
YOUR VERY SOUL.

00:19:27.297 --> 00:19:30.202
AFTER ALL,
IT'S THE ONLY WAY
TO SUPPLY THE GREAT BEAST

00:19:30.202 --> 00:19:32.906
WITH ENOUGH ENERGY
TO WIPE OUT MANKIND.

00:19:32.906 --> 00:19:35.644
BUT WHY STAND HERE
AND TALK ABOUT IT?

00:19:35.644 --> 00:19:38.049
THE SOONER I WIN THIS DUEL,

00:19:38.049 --> 00:19:40.487
THE SOONER
YOU'LL BE GONE FOREVER.

00:19:40.487 --> 00:19:44.160
AND WITH THAT,
I'LL PLACE
TWO CARDS FACEDOWN.

00:19:44.160 --> 00:19:48.200
THEN I'LL PLAY THE MAGIC CARD
PURITY OF THE CEMETERY!

00:19:52.674 --> 00:19:54.979
NOW HERE'S
HOW IT WORKS, PHARAOH.

00:19:54.979 --> 00:19:57.985
YOU LOSE 100
OF YOUR LIFE POINTS
EACH TURN

00:19:57.985 --> 00:20:01.423
FOR EVERY MONSTER
THAT REMAINS
IN YOUR CARD GRAVEYARD,

00:20:01.423 --> 00:20:04.128
AND AS LONG AS MY GRAVEYARD
IS MONSTER-FREE,

00:20:04.128 --> 00:20:05.732
