00:20:05.732 --> 00:20:08.002
Yugi, voice-over:
I HAFTA SEND A MONSTER
OF HIS TO THE GRAVEYARD

00:20:08.002 --> 00:20:09.672
OR I'M A GONER.

00:20:09.672 --> 00:20:11.375
NOW I HAVE
ONE MORE THING

00:20:11.375 --> 00:20:13.044
YOU MAY BE
INTERESTED TO KNOW.

00:20:13.044 --> 00:20:15.248
I HAVE NO INTENTION
OF PLAYING

00:20:15.248 --> 00:20:18.788
MY SEAL OF ORICHALCOS
MAGIC CARD,

00:20:18.788 --> 00:20:20.858
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN
YOU'RE SAFE.

00:20:20.858 --> 00:20:22.762
NOT BY A LONG SHOT.

00:20:22.762 --> 00:20:24.264
YOUR FATE
IS STILL SEALED,

00:20:24.264 --> 00:20:26.100
AND WHEN YOU LOSE
YOUR SOUL,

00:20:26.100 --> 00:20:29.774
IT'LL BE BY
YOUR OWN DOING.

