MY MONSTER
HAS 3000 ATTACK POINTS.

00:20:33.280 --> 00:20:35.781
YOUR MULTICOLORED
POM POM SISTERS

00:20:35.781 --> 00:20:39.184
DON'T EVEN COME CLOSE
TO THE POWER OF MY GUARDIAN.

